5	/* Purpose-built throughput benchmark.
6	 *
7	 * The benchmark walks one fixed token sequence to configurable context
8	 * frontiers, measuring only the newest prefill interval at each frontier.  It
9	 * then snapshots the live session in memory, performs a fixed greedy decode
10	 * run without allowing EOS, restores the snapshot, and continues to the next
11	 * frontier.  Snapshot save/restore time is intentionally outside both timing
12	 * windows.
13	 */
